{"tid":1916792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［大紀元獨家］ 遼寧衛健委下令銷毀武漢肺炎疫情文件","createTime":"2020-03-09T05:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T06:57:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d63f22a245ee148dac8aeb643b7beb23a37c31e8","tid":1916792,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"大紀元獲得一份朝陽市衛健委2月23日發給遼寧省衛健委的機密文件，文件說的是朝陽市衛健委按照省衛健委要求，要求朝陽市交通局、凌源市政府辦公室、北票市政府辦公室、龍城區政府辦公室、雙塔區政府辦公室、喀喇沁左翼蒙古族自治縣政府辦公室、建平縣政府辦公室等相關人員，在傳遞有關武漢肺炎信息時，都已簽署《保密承諾書》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ih2cB9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ih2cB9.png&h=37a4027d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧省衛健委要求朝陽市銷毀內部文件的接收單位列表。（大紀元）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vk9W1vG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvk9W1vG.jpg&h=51fc7549&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72BFJJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72BFJJ2.jpg&h=1be9b2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文件稱，目前，朝陽市交通局、凌源市政府辦公室、龍城區政府辦公室，已經銷毀了相關數據。<br />\n<br />\n文件的附錄部份還包括13份簽名的《保密承諾書》，承諾書內容都是一樣的，只是簽署人不同而已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKdg1vY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKdg1vY.jpg&h=61401c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該承諾書說，對於2月21日發送的保密數據，他們本人承諾：<br />\n<br />\n一，立即銷毀保留在電腦、USB、手機等儲存設備裏的數據文件，以及拍攝的照片、記錄的文字等信息。<br />\n<br />\n二，絕不以任何原因、任何方式複製、使用或向其他人發送上述數據資料。<br />\n<br />\n三，除法律規定的形式外，不得向其它機構和個人洩漏此信息。<br />\n<br />\n如有違反上述內容的，其本人將承擔相應的法律責任和一切後果。<br />\n<br />\n朝陽市下轄：雙塔區、龍城區2個市轄區，北票市、凌源市2個縣級市，朝陽縣、建平縣2個縣，喀喇沁左翼蒙古族自治縣⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-01/65220035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-03-01%2F65220035&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=a38cf6b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-01/65220035</a>"},{"pid":"8e1f5ab05e6975ae6cdc56e8fc69a1bb41f58ae1","tid":1916792,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"大紀元真係朝中有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1088446ee7b7016a623378dad312618b2cf3295","tid":1916792,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"佢點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7cf8283d7bd850aac9af1a105e5e3de5073c7c","tid":1916792,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1088446ee7b7016a623378dad312618b2cf3295","tid":1916792,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"佢點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"大把老友係中南海入面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f29859b3988a38c54fb997f6db719bc1afa6d8a","tid":1916792,"uid":186814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"反習派點會冇留底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}